Try going on my adventure! Find and click the green "Run" button with a play symbol on it and it will start the game. https://replit.com/@AnniesAnalytics/treasure-island-start#main.py 
Functions in this code:
if/elif/else statements, stacked and nested. 
+=1 operator to keep track of score to help guide the path
Print and print(f)
The lower function
OR operator
variables
Inputting ASCII images
 
 
